descriptionNullable: The Daraz dataset is a comprehensive collection of data related to Walmart, one of the largest retail corporations in the world. The dataset contains information about Daraz stores, products, sales, and customers across the Bangladesh. The data is collected over multiple years and covers a wide range of aspects of Daraz's business, including sales volume, inventory, pricing, and promotions.
